title: LF players for Melbourne Lan

embed.description: 2016 Cydus League of Legends Tournament is on Facebook. To connect with 2016 Cydus League of Legends Tournament, join Facebook today.

body:
Looking for players (diamond + highly preferred) for a LAN at Cydus in Melbourne on the 26th of March from 10am till late. Currently have an adc (me) and a support but nothing else set in stone. Want to take it semi seriously and try and win that sweet esports $$$ so a few days of prac beforehand would be good.

PM me or respond here with any interest or shoot me an email
If u can't.

IGN - Pinch
Email - charliewraith@outlook.com 

Cheers,

Pinch

replies.body:
Hey mate, 
D5 atm been playing league for years, and I do live in melbourne. I also have been cydus a few times.

IGN: Pokemon Blue
msg me in there or if you want my email respond here
Play any role tbh, prefer adc/jungle though

Probably a good idea to take your email off of the post (just request those who are interested to add you ingame).
Otherwise, you will become a target for spam/unsolicited emails ♥
It's a seperate email I use just for league related stuff, but thanks :)
